  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for ntfs-3g_ntfsprogs",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for ntfs-3g_ntfsprogs fixes the following issues\n\n- CVE-2026-42616: heap buffer overflow in cat() in cat.c (bsc#1271102).\n- CVE-2026-42617: heap buffer overflow in ntfs_ir_to_ib() in index.c (bsc#1271103).\n- CVE-2026-42618: heap buffer overflow in ntfs_decompress() in compress.c (bsc#1271104).\n- CVE-2026-46569: heap buffer overflow in ntfs_ib_copy_tail() in libntfs-3g/index.c (bsc#1271105).\n- CVE-2026-46570: heap buffer overflow exists in ntfs_index_walk_down() in libntfs-3g/index.c (bsc#1271106).\n- CVE-2026-46571: out-of-bounds read in ntfs_fix_file_name() in libntfs-3g/reparse.c (bsc#1271107).\n- CVE-2026-46572: heap buffer overflow in ntfs_ib_cut_tail() in libntfs-3g/index.c (bsc#1271108).\n- CVE-2026-56135: heap-based buffer overflow in build_inherited_id() in libntfs-3g/security.c (bsc#1271109).\n- CVE-2026-56136: out-of-bounds read in ntfs_ir_nill() in libntfs-3g/index.c (bsc#1271110).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
